      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "QUEEN FLOW (5) shows ability but remains a maiden after six starts. Is better than last start when out of the placings, finishing seventh (29.65) at Sale. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Worth another chance. BOUNDING BETTY (7) was drawn the middle but pinged the lids and led until the final stages, holding on for a place (23.17) at this track in a Maiden over 400m. Can measure up. MATILDA FLAME (4) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (23.53) last time in a Restricted WIN at this track. Form from her last run is proving strong. Worth following up. HOT HONEY (1) did a good job to finish third last time out over 400m at this track (23.31) in a Rank Limit - Maiden, the second top-three finish on the trot.",
